    <item>
      <title>Zephaniah 1</title>
      <link>http://localhost:58357/cir-library/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-01/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:58357/cir-library/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;zephaniah-chapter-1&#34;&gt;Zephaniah Chapter 1&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v1&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; A Message from the LORD to Zephaniah Son of Cushi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v7&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;7&lt;/sup&gt; Be silent in front of the Lord GOD!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v10&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;10&lt;/sup&gt; On that day,&amp;quot; the LORD says,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v11&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;11&lt;/sup&gt; Wail, people in the marketplace,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v12&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;12&lt;/sup&gt; I&amp;rsquo;ll search Jerusalem with lanterns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v13&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;13&lt;/sup&gt; Their wealth will become plunder,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v14&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;14&lt;/sup&gt; That great day of the LORD is near and coming fast,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v17&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;17&lt;/sup&gt; He&amp;rsquo;ll bring such a distress on you&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v18&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;18&lt;/sup&gt; Your silver and gold won&amp;rsquo;t save you&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zephaniah 2</title>
      <link>http://localhost:58357/cir-library/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-02/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:58357/cir-library/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-02/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;zephaniah-chapter-2&#34;&gt;Zephaniah Chapter 2&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v1&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; Get together,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v3&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; Look to him,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v4&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt; Gaza will be abandoned;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v5&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;5&lt;/sup&gt; Misfortune awaits people along the coast,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v6&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;6&lt;/sup&gt; The seacoast will be open range&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v7&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;7&lt;/sup&gt; It will serve as pasture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v10&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;10&lt;/sup&gt; That&amp;rsquo;s what they&amp;rsquo;ll get for their arrogance because they&amp;rsquo;ve taunted the people of the LORD of Hosts. 11He&amp;rsquo;ll terrify them and starve all the gods everywhere. Nations the world over will bow to him, each in their own land.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zephaniah 3</title>
      <link>http://localhost:58357/cir-library/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-03/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:58357/cir-library/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;zephaniah-chapter-3&#34;&gt;Zephaniah Chapter 3&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v1&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; Misfortune awaits the rebellious, defiled, tyrannical city, Jerusalem,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v3&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; Its officials are roaring lions;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v4&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt; Its prophets are reckless, devious men;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v5&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;5&lt;/sup&gt; The LORD is good within it;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v7&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;7&lt;/sup&gt; I said, &amp;lsquo;Surely, they&amp;rsquo;ll respect me now&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v9&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;9&lt;/sup&gt; Then I&amp;rsquo;ll purify the people&amp;rsquo;s lips&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v10&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;10&lt;/sup&gt; From beyond the rivers in Nubia,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v11&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;11&lt;/sup&gt; At that time, you won&amp;rsquo;t need to be ashamed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;verse&#34; id=&#34;v12&#34;&gt;&lt;sup class=&#34;verse-num&#34;&gt;12&lt;/sup&gt; But among you I&amp;rsquo;ll leave humble, common people&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
